"These graves contain the soldiers who fell against the forces of Wyrmhold. May their valiant deeds be remembered forever."

That is, at least, what the pillar used to say. Now, the memorial is only a small pile of charred rubble. The rest of the pillar is strewn about the ruins as a myriad of tiny, blackened rocks.
